snippet.title: We're Tethered Together | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
We're Tethered Together is a cute--yet spooky--indie platformer/puzzle game developed by 10 students.
Play now on Steam! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2578110/Were_Tethered_Together/
